Explain what a token is used for.

/* Tokens are used to store encrypted data and help keep folks whom do not have the dredentials from accessing the users data*/

What steps can you take in your web apps to keep your data secure?

/*https requests, requiring sign on for sensitive data*/

Describe how web servers work.

/*they respond to requests from the front end and send data back if it matches the end points*/


Which HTTP methods can be mapped to the CRUD acronym that we use when interfacing with APIs/Servers.

/*create = post, read = get, update = put, delete = delete*/